タイトル: <font size = 5>Log : NecEpic Quest</font>
投稿者　: Azrael@Nameless&lt;<a href="mailto:azrael@pos.to">azrael@pos.to</a>&gt;
<!-- ドメイン: 210.130.197.74 -->
URL　　 : <a href="http://www1.pos.to/~azrael/">http://www1.pos.to/~azrael/</a>
登録時間:2000年10月15日08時04分</pre>
本文:
<center>
<table width="95%">
<tr bgcolor="#000042"><td>
Venenzi嬢に言われた通り、Kazenに暗黒の術を学びに行きます。<BR>
<BR>
☆ I wish to study the dark arts<BR>
<BR>
Kazen Fecae  looks you up and down, his eyes glowing with a<BR>
soft red light. After a moment be begins to speak though his lips<BR>
do not move. 'You wish to study under me? Perhas, if you<BR>
prove yourself to follow the twisted path. If you prove to be as<BR>
coldhearted as I then I will let you become my servant.<BR>
<BR>
☆ I will prove the twisted path<BR>
<BR>
Kazen Fecae says 'The wandering 'knight' Sir Edwin Motte recently<BR>
slew one of my lesser servants. This foolish knave travels from<BR>
town to town pretending to be 'good.' Separate his head from<BR>
his body and return it to me so I may work my magics upon it.<BR>
This fool will become another plaything for me, even in death.<BR>
<BR>
Sir Edwin Motteの首を取ってくれば良いようです。<BR>
Sir Edwin MotteはFreeportの桟橋横の酒場にいました。<BR>
LVは30代のPaladinで、彼を殺すと以下のFactionの変動がありました。<BR>
<BR>
Your faction standing with Steel Warriors got worse.<BR>
Your faction standing with Guards of Qeynos got worse.<BR>
Your faction standing with Corrupt Qeynos Guards got better.<BR>
Your faction standing with The Freeport Militia got better.<BR>
Your faction standing with Knights of Truth got worse.<BR>
<BR>
☆「Head of Sir Edwin Motte」をKazenに渡す。<BR>
<BR>
Kazen Fecae says 'Excellent!' You watch Kazen hold the head by<BR>
the hair and begin to cast a spell. A flash of darkness centers<BR>
around the head and the eyes of the dead knight open, a terrible<BR>
scream emanating from its lips. 'This poor fool here - I think I<BR>
will keep him in my bag from now on. You have done well, my<BR>
new apprentice. Take this symbol and know that you can do<BR>
other tasks to advance within my apprentice ranks.'<BR>
<BR>
You gain experience!!<BR>
<BR>
「Symbol of the Apprentice」が貰えました。<BR>
手に入れたSymbolの名をEmkelに告げることにより、<BR>
そのランクに応じた秘薬の調達を命じられるようです。
